title: 10cc / Classic Album Selection: Five Albums 1975-1978 (6 CD's)
description:
10cc - Classic Album Selection: Five Albums 1975-1978 (Box Set, 6CD, Mercury, 3704908) - 2012, FLAC (image+.cue), 

Album collection : The composition of this box set includes four studio albums and one double-disc live album, of the most successful "golden" period of the group 10cc. All albums went Gold in the UK. In 1997, the studio albums have been remastered by Roger Wake and bonus tracks have been added . Albums are packed in envelopes type mini LP.
